  "notes": "### LanDock v1.0.1\n\nLanDock turns your Windows PC into a local Wi-Fi hub for your iPhone. Install the Windows MSI, launch LanDock, scan the QR code, and use your iPhone as a local trackpad, keyboard, clipboard bridge, and file drop client.\n\nRelease highlights:\n* Self-contained Windows MSI with bundled Node.js runtime.\n* QR-based local pairing, with Windows Mobile Hotspot support.\n* Recommended hotspot QR target: `192.168.137.1`.\n* iPhone web client with Add to Home Screen support.\n* Clipboard bridge, file transfer, keyboard, and pointer controls.\n\nInstallation:\n* Windows: Download and run the `.msi` installer attached to this release.",
